      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BREAKN' A SWEAT (1) turned in a plain effort last time when sixth at Sale over 435m behind Furious Falcon (25.30) in a Grade 4/5. Placed at his previous run. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings six times from seven attempts. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. PAW YATANA (7) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Rhythmic Energy (24.13) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Boasts two wins from five starts out of this box. Expected to feature again. PAW PRYDI (8) missed the frame latest (25.88) when seventh over 450m at Warrnambool in a Restricted WIN H. Has already won out of this draw. Looks suited here and can measure up. MISS MY BROTHER (2) is a last-start placegetter who will have admirers.",
